{"tid":572243,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手足炒枇杷膏","createTime":"2018-02-25T11:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T22:55:25.000Z","uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2b753694075238b0a76b9d6aa45947f79ee951dc","tid":572243,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"於紐約中國市場經營華人商鋪「珠江」的老闆指出，近日川貝枇杷膏在紐約成為城中熱話，又稱近日高加索地區的客戶都向他要貨，而枇杷膏的平常市價為7.80美元（港幣約61元）。但有報道提到由於產品大受歡迎，有零售網站炒價達至70美元（港幣約547元）一樽。未知炒價是否已經「降溫」，根據零售網站「亞馬遜」，枇杷膏要價港幣約101元一樽，亦比平常市價高，而一盒10包的「枇杷膏便利裝」則售港幣約108元一盒，最誇張是「川貝枇杷糖」，一小盒要價約48港幣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc8f632e5d5ffeecca9c1df6b5298de25742a8e","tid":572243,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"我炒shake  shake薯條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3160dcd737d56915a79b2f3aa27556955df051","tid":572243,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"我有半樽"},{"pid":"da18dfd3b719a1db43be96b18e65d0ed58692ab9","tid":572243,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:46:03.000Z","msg":"今次真係白色珍珠啦"},{"pid":"7a9c2b7117ae8bb0e110f08936c6a82f2ed47007","tid":572243,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"枇杷膏（重倉）"},{"pid":"e11b65cda5063cd1285d64bf8e48f38e82823980","tid":572243,"uid":159435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"而家美國好多人中左流感，咳到痴線。<br />\n啲人話食左止到咳，喉嚨舒服啲。<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n阿姨係紐約人"},{"pid":"f79099049ed08c41ce3f71efcef2a0d66ad97c23","tid":572243,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"我公司得30打，早知入多d貨。<br />\n(利申：開藥房)"},{"pid